<h1 id="references">References</h1>
<!-- markdownlint-enable MD025 -->

<p>The following are reference materials for the IT Strategy team to use.</p>

<p>These materials are meant to be sources of inspiration, guidance, or policies that we need to consider when crafting our strategies.</p>

<p>Some of that content may only be available on GC/ESDC network so if the link doesn’t work externally, we apologize for the inconvenience!</p>

